peer_group_data.peer_selection_rationale:
Selected Chinese e-commerce peer companies based on:
1. BABA (Alibaba) - Dominant Chinese e-commerce marketplace platform
2. JD (JD.com) - Direct competitor in online retail with logistics focus  
3. PDD (PDD Holdings/Pinduoduo) - Group buying e-commerce model
4. BEKE (KE Holdings) - Real estate services platform with online focus
5. YMM (Full Truck Alliance) - Logistics and freight platform

These peers represent the major Chinese internet/e-commerce companies trading as ADRs,
providing comparable business models, regulatory environment, and market dynamics.
All face similar VIE structure risks and China-US regulatory uncertainties.
